Description: In this HIT you are going to select salient areas in the image that mostly represent pets.
Answer.suggestion_texts: Suggestions:- completition code should be shorter - completition code shouldn't be in a separate popup because most browsers will block it as default settings, including Chrome- after drawing the salient, I suggest introducing a key to confirm the selection and make it permanent i.e. [Return]. - Indee, selecting "previous image", the previous selection is not visible anymore which is confusing. I surprised myself wondering: "have i actually finished it or not? Was my selection accepted?".
